OL,3,CWife's devastation after her husband
OL,4,Cdied while she was driving him to
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FA woman whose husband died from a
OL,8,Fheart-attack while she was driving him
OL,9,Fto hospital because no ambulances were
OL,10,Favailable, has said nobody should ever
OL,11,Fagain be put in that position.
OL,13,FIt comes as the Ambulance Service
OL,14,Fagain warns of massive pressures, with
OL,15,Fmany crews still having to wait
OL,16,Fseveral hours outside busy emergency
OL,17,Fdepartments.
