OL,4,Cdied while she was driving him to
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FFather-of-four Willy Darragh died
OL,8,Fduring the 25 minute drive from his
OL,9,Fhouse in Cullybackey to Antrim Area
OL,10,FHospital.
OL,12,FIn 2020, Willy helped to raise more
OL,13,Fthan #70,000 for front-line health
OL,14,Fservices during the pandemic. His
OL,15,Ffundraising efforts earned him a
OL,16,Fnomination for a Pride of Britain Award
OL,18,FA few weeks ago, Willy became a victim
OL,19,Fof the struggling health service he
OL,20,Fhad tried so hard to help.
