OL,3,CWife's devastation after her husband
OL,4,Cdied while she was driving him to
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FHe died in a lay-by on his way to the
OL,8,Femergency department at Antrim Area
OL,9,FHospital after no ambulance was free
OL,10,Fto respond to his wife's first
OL,11,Femergency call.
OL,13,FHis wife Caroline told UTV: "I never
OL,14,Fthought for one minute when I left the
OL,15,Fhouse that night that the outcome
OL,16,Fwould be what we went through in that
OL,17,Flayby.
OL,19,F"I never thought for one minute that
OL,20,Fthat was what was going to happen."
