OL,7,FIt was just a few days before
OL,8,FChristmas when the 53 year-old
OL,9,Fdeveloped chest pains. He had suffered
OL,10,Fa heart-attack 11 years previously and
OL,11,Fknew he needed help quickly.
OL,13,FCaroline, said when she called 999 she
OL,14,Fwas advised it would be quicker to
OL,15,Fbring Willy to hospital herself as a
OL,16,Flarge number of crews were tied up
OL,17,Foutside Emergency Departments.
