OL,7,F"Once I got close to the Seven Towers
OL,8,Froundabout I said to him 'How are we
OL,9,Fdoing now Willy?' and he just said 'it
OL,10,Fis really not good, it is going bad'"
OL,12,F"We got to the dual carriageway and
OL,13,Fthat is whenever he made the big groan
OL,14,Fand clenched his teeth and fell
OL,15,Fforward then.
OL,17,F"There was a guy parked in a van so I
OL,18,Fran to him asking for help and he came
OL,19,Fdown and he phoned 999.
