OL,7,F"They said 'Is there a pulse? You have
OL,8,Fto get him out onto the ground'.
OL,10,F"He took his top part and I took his
OL,11,Flegs and we got him out and left him
OL,12,Fflat on his back and they talked us
OL,13,Fthrough the CPR.
OL,15,F"The guy did it, I was no help at all.
OL,16,FThen the ambulance came straight away.
OL,17,F"
