OL,4,Cdied while she was driving him to
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FNigel Ruddell from the Northern
OL,8,FIreland Ambulance Service said:
OL,9,F"Everybody in our service wants to
OL,10,Fdeliver the best possible service to
OL,11,Fevery single patient, and it is
OL,12,Fincredibly frustrating and incredibly
OL,13,Fdifficult to deal with when, because
OL,14,Fof pressures, we are not able to do
OL,15,Fthat.
OL,17,F"We are sorry that some of our
OL,18,Fpatients are facing that situation
OL,19,Fwhen we are trying our absolute best
OL,20,Fto deliver the best service that we
OL,21,Fcan. "
